Embattled Hawks boss Berning Ntlemeza has been fired with immediate effect. His dismissal was enforced by the Pretoria High Court on Wednesday.Ntlemeza suffered a double-blow on Wednesday when Judges Peter Mabuse Jody Kollapen and Selby Baqwa dismissed his leave to appeal last month s high court decision that his appointment as one of the country s most powerful policemen be reviewed.TMG Digital